headline: Darden (DRI): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q3 Earnings?
summary: Darden’s 21.2% return over the past six months has outpaced the S&P 500 by 7%, and its stock price has climbed to $176.99 per share. This performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
